  "remarks": "Federal State Enterprise Perm Powder Plant is one of the largest enterprises in the Russian defence complex. It produces charges for multiple launch rocket systems and for air defence systems, as well as engine charges for aircraft missiles, systems for cruise missiles and many other weapons. It is owned by the Russian State but according to a decree of the President of the Russian Federation it will be transformed and transferred to the possession of Rostec.",
